{"tid":2029732,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"小心今次玩死自己！求推post","createTime":"2020-05-22T11:21:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T17:01:56.000Z","uid":109345,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"002eee8777eae7f21fc05b9515e6f898ee7f6c81","tid":2029732,"uid":109345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:21:30.000Z","msg":"我知道大家好開心見到今次真正攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但只係第一步 我地永遠唔知對方落緊咩棋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話曬人地propaganda已經成功左咁多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無可能因為今次而失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然對方形勢嚴峻 但我地都唔好得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&mdash;<br />\n趁依家香港仲有價值 我希望大家可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1. 推行動post 唔好太多膠野 （話俾全世界聽我地香港人係唔會接受國安法！）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 國際路線 （繼續twitter Reddit FB YouTube 甚至係國際登報）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 唔好太多幻想 （你以為班藍絲真係驚攬炒？至少我老豆唔驚 ）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4. 加強創意 （希望全方位可以推動國際去制裁中共，甚至！！戰爭！！！）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5. 裝備自己 （運動，抵抗敵軍）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n6. 黃色經濟圈 （繼續支持612；星火；蘋果等）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎5毛推post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9fb33745c8e84e03e4d5c8b980e41992f8a0d2b","tid":2029732,"uid":109345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:22:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c2sz4gZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc2sz4gZ.jpg&h=10823e1c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EKy7EQm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEKy7EQm.jpg&h=2406ca0d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vEOWyao.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvEOWyao.jpg&h=bc4c0717&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55bbf7b66ae980e7b2a68867132d26ecfe0a3b8f","tid":2029732,"uid":109345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:24:32.000Z","msg":"對家仲好勁<br />\n香港人要繼續反抗"},{"pid":"038c7597e3c791ef24715c506aa299f83de9b485","tid":2029732,"uid":13160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:24:49.000Z","msg":"⚠️由于此讯息不符合符合国家安全法规，已被屏蔽。"},{"pid":"bd00069bfc2560fa5abd880b8afaaf010ef8572e","tid":2029732,"uid":109345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:24:58.000Z","msg":"反抗<br />\n報仇<br />\n滅共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aec4cc434a204c23308295ed08a3d4222d52e0f4","tid":2029732,"uid":13160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:25:03.000Z","msg":"⚠️由于此讯息不符合符合国家安全法规，已被屏蔽。"},{"pid":"8e42b61652450458d4b50a2f71ff03e3100df67a","tid":2029732,"uid":13160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:25:15.00